12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 61 O.S. 2021, Section 113.1, as
14 amended by Section 24, Chapter 238, O.S.L. 2022 (61 O.S. Supp. 2024,
15 Section 113.1), is amended to read as follows:
16 Section 113.1. A. A public construction contract shall provide
17 for partial payment based upon work completed. The contract shall
18 provide that up to five percent (5%) of all partial payments made
19 shall be withheld as retainage until the project is fifty percent
20 (50%) complete as determined by the awarding agency. When the
21 awarding public agency determines that the project is at least fifty
22 percent (50%) complete, the retainage amount shall be two and one-
23 half percent (2.5%) with respect to the balance of the work.
